---
title: Lamb and Mint Burger with Cheese and Onion Wedges
description: "What's more British than cheese and onion?" our Chef André asks. "Mint and lamb, perhaps?" he replies. So, go on, get stuck in - and let us know what you think of it!!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/lamb-and-mint-burger-wk50-ad0c1662.jpg
